<p>I have an Array of Strings and I want to select only these Strings which are paths to files:</p>  <p>My path is <code>"~/dlds/some_file.ics"</code> where <code>~/dlds</code> is a symlink to <code>~/archive/downloads</code> on my system. The file has following permissions:</p>  <pre><code>-rw-r--r-- </code></pre>  <p>My code (I tried several variants):</p>  <pre><code>ARGV.select do |string|     File.file? string # returns false     Pathname.new(string).file? # returns false     Pathname.new(string).expand_path.file? # returns false end </code></pre>  <p>I don't know what else to try...</p>  <p>Ruby 2.2.0 or 2.2.2</p>